  schema:name "Donald Trump" ;
  schema:description "American real-estate developer and politician (b. 1946); 45th and 47th President of the United States. The orbit-anchor of the Russian-organized-crime / oligarch-network case, which traces Trump's documented business and political relationships across three threads: Mogilevich → Sater → Bayrock → Trump; the Moscow oligarch network through Aras Agalarov; and the sexual-content / blackmail-infrastructure thread through Epstein, MindGeek/Bergmair, and others." ;
